ZH: 今年我们庄稼得了一个丰收。
EN: This year we had a bountiful harvest on our crops.

ZH: 农民们都希望有一个丰收的季节。
EN: Farmers all hope for a season of abundant harvest.

ZH: 这片土地的丰收是农民们的辛勤劳动的结果。
EN: The abundant harvest on this land is the result of the farmers' hard work.

ZH: 每一次丰收都给我们一种喜悦的感觉。
EN: Every bountiful harvest brings us a joyful feeling.

ZH: 他们努力工作，为了追求更多的丰收。
EN: They work hard to pursue more bountiful harvests.

ZH: 丰收季节是农村最繁忙的时候。
EN: The harvest season is the busiest time in the countryside.

ZH: 农民们为了一个丰收而努力着。
EN: Farmers work hard for a bountiful harvest.

ZH: 每次丰收都像是一个奇迹般的礼物。
EN: Every bountiful harvest feels like a miraculous gift.

ZH: 农民们期盼着一个丰收的季节。
EN: Farmers look forward to a season of abundant harvest.

ZH: 在丰收的季节，人们会一起庆祝。
EN: During the harvest season, people celebrate together.

ZH: 这个季节代表着丰收与收获。
EN: This season symbolizes abundance and harvest.

ZH: 良好的气候条件是丰收的保证。
EN: Good weather conditions are a guarantee for a bountiful harvest.

ZH: 他们庄稼灾年是一个丰收的季节。
EN: For them, this crop failure year is a season of abundant harvest.

ZH: 农民们盼望着来年有一个更大的丰收。
EN: Farmers hope for an even bigger harvest next year.

ZH: 每一次丰收都是农民们辛勤劳动的回报。
EN: Every bountiful harvest is a reward for the farmers' hard work.

ZH: 丰收季节代表着辛勤工作的成果。
EN: The harvest season symbolizes the fruits of hard work.

ZH: 在我们庄稼得到丰收的时候，我们应该感恩。
EN: When our crops have a bountiful harvest, we should be grateful.

ZH: 每个家庭都希望在丰收季节得到好的收成。
EN: Every family hopes for a good harvest during the season of abundance.

ZH: 丰收不仅仅是收成，更是一种成就感。
EN: Bountiful harvest is not just about crops, but also a sense of achievement.

ZH: 我们要为这次丰收感恩。
EN: We should be grateful for this bountiful harvest.
